315
00:26:50,625 --> 00:26:52,875
Hey, now...
What's with the tears...?

316
00:26:52,958 --> 00:26:55,791
I had a damn good run, Seras.

317
00:26:55,875 --> 00:26:57,375
Now, suck my blood...

318
00:26:57,458 --> 00:27:00,083
Take me into yourself
so we can win this fight.

319
00:27:06,666 --> 00:27:07,833
I told you...

320
00:27:07,916 --> 00:27:10,666
Don't waste your tears...
on a mercenary...

321
00:27:19,416 --> 00:27:22,625
You lost those pretty blue eyes
of yours trying to save me.

322
00:27:25,000 --> 00:27:28,458
You lost your arm, too...
What a waste...

323
00:27:29,958 --> 00:27:32,541
Foolish, ma chere...

324
00:27:33,458 --> 00:27:36,291
Another time, maybe...
another place...

325
00:27:38,041 --> 00:27:40,833
You're a rare woman, Seras...

326
00:27:42,583 --> 00:27:47,041
I die so that she
can live... Alright.

327
00:27:58,333 --> 00:27:59,416
Oh God...

328
00:27:59,500 --> 00:28:02,000
