338
00:29:18,000 --> 00:29:19,708
Let's take these bugs...

339
00:29:19,791 --> 00:29:22,041
and crush them
between our fingers!

340
00:29:23,750 --> 00:29:26,791
Such is the death
they deserve...!

341
00:29:26,875 --> 00:29:28,833
The death of an insect!

342
00:29:38,416 --> 00:29:41,250
Not again...! Enough
of this mind-fucking!

343
00:29:42,666 --> 00:29:45,375
You called him a gnat,
didn't you...

344
00:29:47,125 --> 00:29:49,666
You called him... a gnat...!

345
00:29:52,833 --> 00:29:54,458
You'll pay for this.

346
00:30:01,291 --> 00:30:02,916
You will pay!

347
00:30:04,416 --> 00:30:09,125
You're going to pay...
You'll pay!

348
00:31:19,125 --> 00:31:22,541
Thank you, Captain...
Rest in peace.

349
00:31:23,041 --> 00:31:24,541
But not yet...

350
00:31:27,208 --> 00:31:28,625
Not yet!

351
00:31:31,416 --> 00:31:32,958
What's going on...?

352
00:31:33,541 --> 00:31:35,041
She broke Zorin's spell...!

353
00:31:35,125 --> 00:31:37,083
I did what you told me.

354
00:31:37,166 --> 00:31:39,875
And in return you're
going to help me...

355
00:31:39,958 --> 00:31:41,916
send these Nazis to hell!

356
00:31:42,625 --> 00:31:45,833
What? How is this possible...?!

357
00:31:45,916 --> 00:31:50,083
They're trembling...! These
battle-hardened Waffen-SS...

358
00:31:50,166 --> 00:31:53,333
these vampires, who charged
into gunfire and grenades

359
00:31:53,416 --> 00:31:55,291
without a moment's
hesitation...!

360
00:31:56,708 --> 00:31:59,958
They're ready to piss themselves
at the sight of a girl!

361
00:32:00,041 --> 00:32:05,333
One stupid, weak little girl
who's more dead than alive!

362
00:32:05,416 --> 00:32:08,416
What the hell's
going on...?! Verdammt!

363
00:32:10,708 --> 00:32:12,416
Open fire! Everyone--shoot!

364
00:32:39,000 --> 00:32:41,708
It's not possible...
It's bullscheise!

365
00:32:41,791 --> 00:32:43,875
