straight for me!

367
00:33:20,333 --> 00:33:22,166
Even if I were about to die...

368
00:33:22,250 --> 00:33:25,916
I wouldn't drink a single
goddamn drop of your evil blood!

369
00:33:26,000 --> 00:33:28,750
I don't want you...
inside of me!

370
00:33:41,750 --> 00:33:44,125
Let's go... deeper!

371
00:33:44,208 --> 00:33:49,000
That's it...!
Even deeper... Yes, take it...

372
00:33:49,083 --> 00:33:51,166
Show me your pain!

373
00:33:52,833 --> 00:33:56,875
What am I looking at...?
These aren't her memories...

374
00:33:57,708 --> 00:33:59,458
What's going on here...?

375
00:33:59,541 --> 00:34:03,250
This isn't right!--everything's
in disarray...!

376
00:34:03,333 --> 00:34:06,500
Why can't I go any
deeper into her head?!

377
00:34:06,875 --> 00:34:09,583
It's like these fucking
memories are protecting her!

378
00:34:12,083 --> 00:34:15,208
It's him...!
That arrogant mercenary...!

379
00:34:15,291 --> 00:34:18,791
That goddamned gnat!

380
00:34:18,875 --> 00:34:22,333
Blood is the currency of
the soul, the vehicle of life.

381
00:34:22,416 --> 00:34:25,041
Having blood offered...

382
00:34:25,125 --> 00:34:29,458
is a very different
experience... than taking it!

383
00:34:30,958 --> 00:34:33,666
Are you okay...? You look awful!

384
00:34:33,750 --> 00:34:35,916
How are you here?

385
00:34:36,000 --> 00:34:38,250
Don't act so surprised,
Zorin...! Whoa!

386
00:34:38,333 --> 00:34:42,625
As they say... I am
everywhere...! And nowhere!

387
00:34:42,708 --> 00:34:46,250
I am here...! To deliver a
message from the Major...

388
00:34:46,333 --> 00:34:49,208
Straight from our
fearless leader's mouth!

389
00:34:49,291 --> 00:34:53,125
"Every soldier dreams of leading
the charge against the foe.

390
00:34:53,208 --> 00:34:54,583
Such is their reward.

391
00:34:54,666 --> 00:34:56,416
But the long-suffering
commander--

392
00:34:56,500 --> 00:34:58,583
