when they fail?

393
00:34:58,666 --> 00:35:00,791
When they go against
orders, lose men,

394
00:35:00,875 --> 00:35:02,833
and prove themselves inept?"

395
00:35:02,916 --> 00:35:04,291
That's the message...!

396
00:35:04,375 --> 00:35:05,875
Under normal circumstances,

397
00:35:05,958 --> 00:35:08,833
they would have burned you to
a crisp long before now... but!

398
00:35:08,916 --> 00:35:11,416
The Major and Doc
got their hands

399
00:35:11,500 --> 00:35:13,208
