411
00:37:13,875 --> 00:37:16,833
Heading out?
But where is there to go?

412
00:37:16,916 --> 00:37:20,416
He told me... to drink him in...

413
00:37:20,500 --> 00:37:23,333
so that we could win this fight.

414
00:37:27,916 --> 00:37:31,833
And now... I think the Captain
and I are only getting started.

415
00:37:33,333 --> 00:37:35,208
I-Inside...?

416
00:37:37,166 --> 00:37:39,291
Right here... Captain...

417
00:37:39,375 --> 00:37:42,291
This is where you
made your last stand.

418
00:37:42,375 --> 00:37:46,375
You're dead...
but you're not gone...

419
00:37:46,458 --> 00:37:48,500
'Cause you're
inside of that girl.

420
00:37:50,916 --> 00:37:52,375
One last thing...

421
00:38:04,750 --> 00:38:06,250
Thanks, sir.

422
00:38:06,333 --> 00:38:07,583
Sir!

423
00:38:26,125 --> 00:38:31,375
The dawn is finally breaking...
come to slay the night.

424
00:38:31,458 --> 00:38:35,416
Undaunted by the light of
the sun, she speeds away...

425
00:38:35,500 --> 00:38:39,416
as though fired
from a bow drawn taut.

426
00:38:40,083 --> 00:38:41,625
