427
00:38:43,458 --> 00:38:45,500
For a raid upon the morn!

428
00:43:55,166 --> 00:43:59,708
This is it... What my
eyes have so longed for...

429
00:44:00,333 --> 00:44:03,458
Ah, what a sight...

430
00:44:03,541 --> 00:44:06,166
For what it's worth,
Zorin's dead, sir.

431
00:44:06,250 --> 00:44:08,500
Killed by a gnat.

432
00:44:08,583 --> 00:44:15,458
Well, that's hardly a surprise.
Watch how it burns, boy.

433
00:44:15,541 --> 00:44:18,750
Like the end of the
Gotterdammerung...

434
00:44:20,000 --> 00:44:22,750
Major, you're such a meanie...

435
00:44:22,833 --> 00:44:25,750
