from without end.

441
00:44:48,333 --> 00:44:51,000
How many days of
wild aspiration...

442
00:44:51,083 --> 00:44:53,375
how many nights
of black entropy...

443
00:44:53,458 --> 00:44:57,208
have I slain to
witness this triumph...?

444
00:44:57,291 --> 00:45:00,208
