445
00:45:00,291 --> 00:45:04,416
together with our victory!

446
00:45:37,041 --> 00:45:41,625
A private army of Nazis
from Germany's Third Reich.

447
00:45:41,708 --> 00:45:43,250
"The Last Battalion".

448
00:45:43,333 --> 00:45:48,125
A division of Waffen-SS panzer
grenadiers turned into vampires.

449
00:45:48,208 --> 00:45:51,875
