of their number remain.

450
00:45:54,541 --> 00:45:57,625
The knights of the ninth
airborne mobile crusade,

451
00:45:57,708 --> 00:46:01,583
sent forth by the Vatican to
serve Archbishop Maxwell.

452
00:46:01,666 --> 00:46:02,958
Two-thousand nine-hundred

453
00:46:03,041 --> 00:46:05,541
and seventy-five of
their number remain.

454
00:46:05,625 --> 00:46:09,583
Her Majesty's Hellsing
Organization of England.

455
00:46:09,666 --> 00:46:12,125
