their number remain.

456
00:46:13,916 --> 00:46:17,250
Release control
art-restriction level zero.

457
00:46:17,333 --> 00:46:21,208
Acknowledged.
As you wish, my master.

458
00:46:27,666 --> 00:46:29,541
Return to our shores,

459
00:46:29,625 --> 00:46:33,375
and bury our foes under
the darkness within you!

460
00:46:33,458 --> 00:46:34,750
Now!

